WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.339
Today, C++ is one of the most important programming languages in the world.

00:00:05.339 --> 00:00:11.745
Millions of C++ developers use C++ to develop on embedded systems,

00:00:11.744 --> 00:00:13.529
the Internet of Things,

00:00:13.529 --> 00:00:16.439
automobiles, and high-performance servers.

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:18.570
Even after 40 years,

00:00:18.570 --> 00:00:21.929
the user base of C++ continues to grow as

00:00:21.929 --> 00:00:27.789
more software developers find different applications for the C++ programming language.

